'''天主教富爾達教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Fuldensis}}；{{lang-de|Bistum Fulda}}）是[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]]以[[德國|德國]]中部[[富爾達|富爾達]]為中心的一個[[教區|教區]]，屬[[天主教帕德伯恩總教區|帕德伯恩總教區]]。

[[File:Karte_Bistum_Fulda.png|thumb]]
2011年，有教友409,300 人，佔轄區總人口17.8%、306個堂區、351名司鐸、54名執事、104名修士、265名修女。

[[聖波尼法爵|聖波尼法爵]]744年在當地建立了一家[[修道院|修道院]]。1752年10月9日改組成教區。1222年至1802年間院長（後期是主教）也是[[采邑主教|轄區的世俗統治者]]。現任主教為彌額爾·格伯（Michael Gerber）<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 13.12.2018 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/12/13/181213d.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-07-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190716045238/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/12/13/181213d.html |archivedate=2019-07-16 |language=en |date=2018-12-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，輔理主教為{{link-de|卡爾海因茨·迪茨|Karlheinz Diez}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 13.07.2004 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2004/07/13/0352/01156.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-07-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190716045319/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2004/07/13/0352/01156.html |archivedate=2019-07-16 |language=it |date=2004-07-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休主教為{{link-en|海因茨·若瑟·阿爾格爾米森|Heinz Josef Algermissen}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 05.06.2018 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/06/05/180605a.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-07-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190716044100/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/06/05/180605a.html |archivedate=2019-07-16 |language=en |date=2018-06-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

